==自然史==
亞瓦派縣擁有無數植物物种和动物物种。例如，大量[[麻黃|麻黃]]和[[金雞菊屬|金雞菊屬]]植物都可於亞瓦派縣內找到。<ref>T. Kearney, Robert H. Peebles and Elizabeth McClintock.  ''Arizona Flora''.  2nd ed.  [[Berkeley,_California|Berkeley]]: [[University_of_California|U of California P]], 1940, 61 et seq. ISBN 978-0-520-00637-9, ISBN 978-0-520-00637-9</ref>亞瓦派縣也擁有不少身為[[近危物種|近危物種]]的[[华盛顿棕榈|华盛顿棕榈]]。<ref>C. Michael Hogan. 2009. [http://globaltwitcher.auderis.se/artspec_information.asp?thingid=90942 ''California Fan Palm: Washingtonia filifera'', GlobalTwitcher.com, ed. Nicklas Stromberg] {{Wayback|url=http://globaltwitcher.auderis.se/artspec_information.asp?thingid=90942 |date=20090930184850 }}</ref>

